originalText.text: Horrible doctor. Completely dismissed my dad’s aching stomach, wheezing, high fever and pain level. She sent him home with no medications, a PCR Covid test and told him to go to his PCP. Well Doctor.. my dad is now 3 days after your HORRIBLE VISIT in EMERGENCY SURGERY with a bowel obstruction and hole in his abdomen leaking air. She forced a nasal swab so far up my dad’s nose with no bedside manner what so ever. He already tested negative with a rapid test done only minutes before by the nurse. I don’t know where these doctors are coming from but they need to do better. Peoples lives are at stake including my dad’s right now due to this doctor’s ignorance.
